{"tid":1431184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣部「拉攏民意」- 派紙巾","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:01:21.000Z","uid":287136,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f706d0bf0b6bb8b660e6ccba6d7d85171164319","tid":1431184,"uid":287136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩諗起可以吸引中立人士/老人/淺藍既手段 - 免費紙巾。例如以下呢個post<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/80smomentum/posts/1727728207508230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F80smomentum%2Fposts%2F1727728207508230&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=fd40c784\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/80smomentum/posts/1727728207508230</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然會有成本，但派紙巾既效益肯定高過派傳單。可以定期請人於繁忙時段於各區連濃牆免費派，重點係可以改善抗爭者係中立人士心目中既形象，吸引更多人到連濃牆睇，而且可以將我地既訊息帶番去所人人既屋企。有冇巴士覺得可行？"},{"pid":"16e53661ea6f618179d68ea1a2065c16206be57b","tid":1431184,"uid":287136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1924241e68bc4e4e48cde408ce4fc8b5538e94ab","tid":1431184,"uid":287136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:38:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fbd3ec9b0d1582f6560b46c1d5b121b93359c567","tid":1431184,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"好橋要推"},{"pid":"241101a220816347b697eb2e13f98c52980460c4","tid":1431184,"uid":287136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5551689a79b0fc41607c9f61ef2a566027866b32","tid":1431184,"uid":263525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:40:02.000Z","msg":"反對，極反對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太易俾對家做文章！<br />\n<br />\n紙巾加料，大陸好多。<br />\n<br />\n派完，自己友要撐都撐左，對家只會戒心大左。"},{"pid":"279de2be8f4bd64c4c59cf9a3988d7b25b044c63","tid":1431184,"uid":287136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5551689a79b0fc41607c9f61ef2a566027866b32","tid":